http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/BSF-apprehends-suspect-from-border-area/article13993143.ece

A man, allegedly moving suspiciously near a BSF post in the border area of Dera Baba Nanak here in Gurdaspur district, was apprehended on Sunday and handed over to police.The man, identified as Harpreet Singh alias Honey, was wearing a trouser similar to army fatigue and was allegedly hiding in the bushes when he was caught by BSF, SHO of Dera Baba Nanak Paramjit Singh said.BSF seized his mobile phone which was allegedly used to take pictures of army tanks and government buildings, Mr. Singh said.The man was handed over to the police, he said, adding that investigation was going on.-PTI